Retellings of the stories of *Dracula*, *Frankenstein*, and more in the form of &amp;#34;word find&amp;#34; puzzles. Each chapter of each book is represented as a word find with specific key words plus a secret message at the end! In French. Created with Jonathan Lessard.
&lt;h4 id="links"&gt;Links&lt;/h4&gt;
